data.description: Location Location, Location! Enjoy easy living and affordable luxury in the highly sought after Spartanburg County School district 5. Easy access to Greenville and Spartanburg! Less than 3 miles to Hwy I-85, BMW Manufacturing and Tyger River Ball Park and less than 10 minutes to Retail shopping in the Five Forks area. This like new Craftsman style home is a spacious open 4BR/2.5BA floor plan. Formal living and dining rooms with beautiful moldings, large open family room with a cozy gas log fireplace. Lots of counter space in this big, open kitchen featuring beautiful granite counter tops with custom tile back-splash, natural gas stove, and a center island. Sunlit breakfast nook, stunning arches throughout, 9’ceilings on main floor, coffered ceiling in dining room and vaulted ceilings in all upstairs bedrooms. Extra large (20'x26') master suite, that features vaulted ceiling, beautiful tile bathroom and huge walk-in closet. Enjoy the relaxing or entertaining on the screened in porch in the privacy of your fenced backyard. Make sure to take note of the highly efficient tank less hot water heater as well. If you are looking for luxury and a great location, look no further. Make your appointment to see this beautiful home today!
